videos.headline: Florida defense gets second fumble recovery of season
videos.description: Spencer Brown fails to secure the football and Florida's defense recovers the ball in good field position, which would lead to a field goal.

videos.headline: UAB tries for big play and it backfires
videos.description: Chauncey Gardner Jr. intercepts Alabama Birmingham's Kylen Binn's deep pass and returns it for 42 yards to give Florida's offense a short field.

videos.headline: Florida capitalizes off of turnover
videos.description: After kicking three field goals,  Florida finds the end zone when Feleipe Franks hooks up with C'yontai Lewis for an 11-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Shannon not happy with receivers in first half
videos.description: Florida interim head coach Randy Shannon is pleased with the Gators' defense but says his receivers need to make more catches.

videos.headline: Florida's Goolsby snags first TD pass of the season
videos.description: Feleipe Franks throws a strike to DeAndre Goolsby for a 13-yard touchdown to put the Gators up 26-0 in the third quarter.

videos.headline: Florida's Perine beats defenders in foot race to the end zone
videos.description: Lamical Perine caps off a 78-yard drive with a 15-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: UAB gets into end zone with 74-yard TD
videos.description: A.J. Erdely throws a dime to Xavier Ubosi for a 74-yard touchdown catch.

videos.headline: Shannon gives kudos to team, coaching staff after win
videos.description: Florida interim coach Randy Shannon says he's "proud" of the Gators for improving their red-zone offense and getting into the end zone.

videos.headline: Franks: Win over UAB helps Florida's confidence
videos.description: QB Feleipe Franks says it was good for the offense to see some players pick up their first touchdowns of the season in Florida's 36-7 win.

videos.headline: First-half turnovers titled game in Florida's favor
videos.description: Matt Stinchcomb says Florida's defense set the tone early in the game and stifled Alabama Birmingham's offense.
